{"tid":1572384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《召喚》和理非你地去晒邊？其實你地仲有好多野可以做！","createTime":"2019-09-15T16:12:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T18:27:35.000Z","uid":270629,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"6a17572de1a940aff3af334161f7dc78ea75dcd6","tid":1572384,"uid":270629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:12:48.000Z","msg":"和理非呢個月真係弱左好多囉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自從818之後，已經無咩夠力嘅代表作！<br />\n你地唔好同我講你地因爲條女子出黎撒就收左貨收晒皮！<br />\n唔好同我講好無力，唔知除左出黎唱歌仔同鳩行之外仲可以做咩！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">明明仲有好多野可以做！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你地知唔知甘地點令印度獨立？<br />\n知唔知馬丁路德金點爭取黑人平權？<br />\n除左遊行集會，<br />\n其中好重要嘅就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不合作運動！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真，唱歌再唱落去，<br />\n反而令到大家發洩左道氣，仲無咁嬲...<br />\n你地一個二個要儲住啲<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">怒氣</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n集合啲能量做啲<strong>有意義有影響力嘅野！</strong><br />\n<br />\n唔好再匿埋喺屋企睇直播做冷氣軍師鬧感覺無力，<br />\n星期六日出去啲大商場尢其係黨鐵啲場，<br />\n幫佢搞旺個場 ，<br />\n搞到啲行街食飯嘅市民都記起要將榮光歸香港，<br />\n無晒心機消費！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">零售一靠自由行，二靠周末本地消費，香港少左自由行加上人仔跌到仆街，零售都已經跌一大截，大家識做就再幫佢推一推，如果本地消費都唔生性，又要交貴租，咁基本上就一定蝕錢...租戶無生意蝕錢，最後一定影響租金收入，咁到時商家同黨鐵就燒到埋身，自然施壓俾政府！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好以為要好耐，其實好多零售都得好少營利...<br />\n連續三四個月做唔到營業額，就好易收皮，飲食業更快。<br />\n總之fixed cost越多，即係租金人工買貨嗰啲...<br />\n死得越快！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922</span></span>你地全部同我出晒黎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沙田新城市+連城，集體塞商場！<br />\n罷買阻塞唱歌人鏈貪食蛇！<br />\n打游擊但唔快閃，玩足佢一日！<br />\n又有冷氣又唔使申請Nono!<br />\n<br />\n等你地之前做自由行生意做得咁開心...<br />\n放狗入黎咬人咬得咁高興...<br />\n黨鐵封站封得咁輕鬆...<br />\n係時候後果自負<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n【 突發】和理塞 商場篇 終於出爐!922第一彈約定你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563867\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563867</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eEpVQiK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeEpVQiK.png&h=e65fed9b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QorUmqq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQorUmqq.png&h=d9073e13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cURMWYM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcURMWYM.png&h=3607bf0d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MQmpJDN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMQmpJDN.png&h=7452ff30&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/APZuULs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAPZuULs.jpg&h=9cfff29e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ESNoZb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FESNoZb8.jpg&h=b4118780&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b54cd4a942f0ab3518ef47950516a484af864da","tid":1572384,"uid":305794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:13:38.000Z","msg":"［極重要］全民錫春袋！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1572107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1572107</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eba82cd8ecc309b8c3